        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">HTTP请求在协议栈中的封装过程：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">应用层: GET /index.html HTTP/1.1
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">传输层: [TCP头部 | HTTP数据]          端口号标识进程
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">网络层: [IP头部 | TCP头部 | HTTP数据]  IP地址标识主机
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">链路层: [MAC头部 | IP头部 | TCP头部 | HTTP数据 | FCS]  MAC地址标识网卡
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">物理层: 01010101... 电信号/光信号</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
